8. PRIVACY
   This software reads process memory exclusively from YARG (yarg.exe) and
   GH World Tour: Definitive Edition (GHWT_Definitive.exe) for the sole purpose
   of detecting in-game star power state. No data is collected, stored, transmitted,
   or sent to any external server or to the author. All communication is strictly
   local (localhost only). Forks must disclose any additional processes they read
   or any data they transmit.

